        </DOC>
        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_2095_9_0</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>At a University Centre within a College by any chance?</TEXT>
        </DOC>
        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_2095_10_0</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>Snap, although they don't let me loose with L3's other than for recruitment!</TEXT>
        </DOC>
        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_2095_10_1</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>I lead the Criminology (L5) and Criminal Justice (L6) modules within a Social Studies degree.</TEXT>
        </DOC>
        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_2095_10_2</DOCNO>
