        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_2095_13_1</DOCNO>
            	<TEXT>Over the past few days, I've read an increasing number of commentaries regarding a significant amount of amendments (additions) being made to the Police, Crime, Sentencing and Courts Bill following its passage through both the House of Commons and House of Lords.</TEXT>
        </DOC>
        <DOC>
            	<DOCNO>s_2095_13_2</DOCNO>
